ts 可选；引用角色校验  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":208,"content":"- [x] 包内卡新建/删除/保存与 conf+cards 磁盘同步  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":209,"content":"- [x] ExitCondition v1 写 condition；critical roundtrip  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":210,"content":"- [x] 全库锚点；无 participants 双轨  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":211,"content":"- [x] 资源落盘；资产引用真源；头像直传  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":212,"content":"- [x] 包 meta 最小可编；Schedule 分工明确  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":213,"content":"- [x] 遗留角色清理；UX 债完成；包可搜索新建  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":214,"content":"- [x] 保存 validate 阻断 + 错误定位 v1  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":215,"content":"- [x] quality:engine + quality:studio 全绿  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":216,"content":"- [x] docs/AI 已更新  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":217,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":218,"content":"收口后 **不要在本文件继续加任务**（S8-19 可选不算阻塞收口）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":219,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":220,"content":"---","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":221,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":222,"content":"## 4. 任务 ↔ 需求映射","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":223,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":224,"content":"| 任务 | 细化修改8_需求 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":225,"content":"|------|----------------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":226,"content":"| V2-S8-1–3 | §2.0–§2.1 · 阶段 A |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":227,"content":"| V2-S8-4–6 | §2.2–§2.3 · 阶段 B |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":228,"content":"| V2-S8-7–9 | §2.4 · 阶段 C |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":229,"content":"| V2-S8-10–11 | §2.5 · 阶段 D |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":230,"content":"| V2-S8-12–14 | §2.6 · 阶段 E |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":231,"content":"| V2-S8-15–16 | §2.7 · 阶段 F |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":232,"content":"| V2-S8-17 | §2.8–§2.9 · 阶段 G（UX） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":233,"content":"| V2-S8-18 | §2.10 · 阶段 G（validate+收口） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":234,"content":"| V2-S8-19 | §1.2 可选 · 非阻塞 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":235,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":236,"content":"---","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":237,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":238,"content":"## 5. 给执行者的提醒","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":239,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":240,"content":"- **先 `--dry-run`** 再正式跑 gbx。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":241,"content":"- **严格 A→B→C**：condition 写盘依赖 callCardProjectionMapper（S8-8/9）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":242,"content":"- **E 在 validate 定位前**：S8-18 validate 才能真实拦 ASSET_*。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":243,"content":"- **S8-17 删角色**：必须先迁移 golden_handoff。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":244,"content":"- **S8-19** 仅在有余力时做；不做不阻塞 S8-18 收口。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":245,"content":"- 脏树 checkpoint 会 BLOCKED。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]}],"totalLines":201,"totalMatchedLines":4,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-cbf539ad-8c8c-47e1-85f6-39fa7bf6fe8b-2\nfc_7237b99f-7a97-9b4a-bac4-2fa139f6beac_1","startedAtMs":"1784771881588","completedAtMs":"1784771881826"},"model_call_id":"e5bbcebc-0eba-4630-8c3b-ab4089fe4c37-1-58tl","session_id":"16f20ac7-7072-4bd1-aa0d-684cfa8362c1","timestamp_ms":1784771881786}
